# =============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS - Defines code ownership and required reviewers
# =============================================================================
# When a PR touches files matching a pattern, the listed owners are
# automatically requested for review. With branch protection enabled,
# their approval is REQUIRED before merge.
#
# Teams should be created in GitHub: Settings → Teams
# Example: @onelasha/backend-team, @onelasha/frontend-team, @onelasha/platform-team
# =============================================================================

